{
  "stem": "7093.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She remained our kapo until, during the whole time in Auschwitz and during my whole time that I was in camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she and I never had any trouble or any dealings actually with her anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was put on trial afterwards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But luckily I-- well I wasn't asked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I didn't-- I certainly wouldn't have put her on trial on my account.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now she-- that was the one incident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the other incident was that while we were outside and we weren't allowed into the barrack, and we were grilling under the sun.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And very many people of course were completely burnt, and blistering, and in terrible agony.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Somebody found a piece of glass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And with the piece of glass they made a circle, drew a circle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then-- I never believed in anything spiritualism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they, they started to do something, moving and reading odd things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And suddenly-- and I was just standing there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And suddenly one of them shouted, Hitler has been assassinated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now we could not have got news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was no way we could have got news at that point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Later on, there was possibility.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But at that point there was absolutely no possibility.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were not taken out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We didn't have occasion to speak to anyone except to-- I mean, amongst us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "To Germans you had no occasion to speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was Hitler has been assassinated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for some reason or other, and again I come back again, I was obsessed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, no, he was not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was only-- he wasn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing happened to him or he was-- I don't remember now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did I say he was hurt?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But anyway, he didn't die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was nearly lynched because there was big scream, I mean, screaming Hitler has been assassinated.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
